channel.title: [DELTA] The First Generation - Where Creation Was Born! [DELTA]
channel.description:
[center][font=Arial][size=24pt]The First Generation - Where Creation Was Born![/size][/font][/center] This is just a project so I can learn Java. Support me!
[size=18pt]Welcome to the development thread of: The First Generation[/size] We aim to plead players. This ain't no PI server. This is Old School! [hr]
[b][center][size=11pt][u]What?[/u][/size][/center] [size=12pt]What? I hear you cry. The First Generation. Well, there's too many PI's. They're advancing everyday. From Torva to a new custom model. Why? The fun isn't in the items, it's the joy of doing hard work. Old School, everyone loved it. Where has our happiness gone? The awesome feeling of when you get your 99's, the joy of PKing with friends. The fun of Events and Drop Parties. It's all gone. Until now...[/size] [hr] [center][u][size=13pt]Who?[/size][/u][/center] [size=14pt]The Development team consists of 3 people, they are listed below:[/size]
[b][center]Main Owner/Developer - [b]Sarwar[/b] (me) Developer[b] - Zeanr[/b] Developer[b] - ---[/b] [/center] [hr] [center][u][size=12pt]Information[/size][/u][/center] Some information to the people that are looking forward to play:
[size=24pt] [ul][li]The server will be based off Delta [/li][li]A unique point system[/li]
[li]Some skills will be re-written by me[/li] [li]All old school skills will be trainable.[/li]
[li]Same old training[/li]
[li]Same old shops[/li]
[li]Bad players will be dealt with ASAP![/li]
[li]Fun Event's every once in a while[/li]
[li]Tutorial Island[/li][/ul]
[hr]
